If they ask â€œWhich is best?â€ â€” say:

> "Explicit Wait is the best practice for dynamic web pages because itâ€™s targeted and efficient. Implicit Wait can be used as a fallback for all element searches, but Thread.sleep() should be avoided in real automation scripts as it causes unnecessary delays."

